Introduction

SEVEN TO EIGHT is an upcoming 7-member global boy group under TEN Entertainment. The group consists of Chi Wen, Mei Tsiang, Pang Ee Xiang, Park Jin Woo, Xue Jun, Jagger and D'om. They are based in Taiwan and Korea and was formed through the survival show SCOOL. They are set to debut sometime in 2025.
